{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"他們互相詢問，詢問什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"詢問那重大的消息，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"就是他們所爭論的消息。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"絕不然！他們將來就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"絕不然，他們將來就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"難道我沒有使大地如搖籃，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"使山巒如木梉嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"我曾把你們造成配偶，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"我曾使你們從睡眠中得到休息，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"我曾以黑夜為帷幕，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"我以白晝供謀生，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"我曾在你們上面建造了七層堅固的天，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"我創造一盞明燈，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"我從含水的雲裡，降下滂沱大雨，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"以便我借它而生出百谷和草木，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"以及茂密的園圃。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"判決之日，確是指定的日期，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"在那日，號角將被吹嚮，你們就成群而來；"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"天將被開辟，有許多門戶；"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"山巒將被移動，而變成幻影；"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"火獄確是伺候著，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"它是悖逆者的歸宿；"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"他們將在其中逗留長久的時期。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他們在其中不能睡眠，不得飲料，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"只飲沸水和膿汁。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"那是一個很適當的報酬。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"他們的確不怕清算，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他們曾否認我的跡象，"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"我曾將萬事記錄在一本天經裡。"},{"SurahNumber":78,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"（將對他們說：）「你們嘗試吧！我只增加你們所受的刑罰。」"}]}